comment: * Listener for observing the completion of a PixelCopy request.

methods.name: void onPixelCopyFinished(@CopyResultStatus int copyResult)
methods.comment: * Callback for when a pixel copy request has completed. This will be called * regardless of whether the copy succeeded or failed. * * @param copyResult Contains the resulting status of the copy request. * This will either be {@link PixelCopy#SUCCESS} or one of the * PixelCopy.ERROR_* values.
